# Thanks & Giving Speakeasy 2026 — Givebutter Implementation Guide

> **EdenHill Communities** · November 20, 2026 · McKenna Center

A complete, copy-ready implementation guide for building the Thanks & Giving Speakeasy fundraising campaign in [Givebutter](https://givebutter.com). Includes all campaign copy, ticket configurations, sponsorship tiers, underwriting opportunities, SEO metadata, email templates, and a pre-launch checklist.

---

## Quick Start

Open `index.html` in any browser. Every copy block has a **one-click copy button** — paste directly into Givebutter's campaign editor.

To host as a live reference page, deploy to GitHub Pages:

```
Settings → Pages → Source: main branch → / (root)
```

Your guide will be live at `https://<org>.github.io/edenhill-givebutter/`

